# 20. アイドル新鋭隊

Airi: It's not just Minori's. Our Untitled tracks are glowing too.
Miku: Now that you've found your true feelings, they're about to give birth to a new song.
Miku: Songs are all made of the true feelings within people's hearts.
Minori: True feelings? What do you mean, our true feelings?
Airi: Hehe. It makes sense that you might not get it. After all, you've had them from the very beginning.
Shizuku: That's right. Even when we were close to losing sight of ours, you always kept these feelings close.
Minori: What?
Haruka: The desire to become an idol.
Haruka: To be the kind who gives hope to everyone around them. Those are my—no, those are our true feelings.
Haruka: Thank you. If it weren't for all of you, I wouldn't have been able to move forward.
Haruka: Momoi, Shizuku, thank you.
Haruka: And thank you so much, Minori.
Minori: No, p-please, don't thank me! Momoi and Hinomori had to help me the entire time!
Airi: That's not true. You're the reason all of us were able to rediscover our true feelings, Minori.
Shizuku: That's right. Thank you for helping us remember what was most important, Minori.
Haruka: Minori, it's because you took my hand and pulled me back up that I was able to reclaim this feeling.
Minori: Haruka... Momoi... Hinomori...
Miku: Hey, what do you say we all sing this song together?! Do you mind if I join you?
Minori: Huh?! Sing with Miku?!
Minori: Being able to sing with you would be wonderful!
Rin: Great! Why don't I get things warmed up as the MC, then! Let's put on a great show, everyone!
Miku: Let's sing together!
Minori: *Huff*... *Huff*... That was so much fun!
Airi: That was my best performance yet! Being an idol really is the best!
Shizuku: I wonder how long it's been since I felt like this.
Haruka: .....
Haruka: It really is a beautiful sight.
Airi: Huh? The name of the song changed.
Minori: What? Oh, you're right! Let's see... Newly Edgy Idols?
Minori: Is this the song we just sang?
Miku: Yep! It's the song born from everyone's feelings!
Haruka: Hehe. It was so fun and upbeat. A perfect song for looking forward to the future, Minori!
Minori: Yeah!
Minori: Miku. Rin. Thank you so much. Thanks to you, our feelings were finally able to reach Haruka!
Haruka: Yes. Miku, Rin, thank you for giving me the push I needed.
Haruka: I have no way of thanking you enough. I don't know what to say.
Miku: That fact that you all found your feelings and sang them for us is more than enough to make us happy!
Rin: That's right! Oh, but we hope you'll come back and sing for us again some time.
Miku: I agree. After all, this is your SEKAI. Come back and visit any time.
Rin: Especially if you're ever feeling down! We'll make sure to cheer you right back up♪
Airi: Of course. Thank you, Rin.
Shizuku: Rin, you helped Airi and I when we needed it most. Thank you so much.
Rin: Hehehe. You're welcome.
Minori: Um, Miku, Rin, that show we just did was so much fun!
Minori: Would it be okay if we performed with you again sometime?
Miku & Rin: Of course!
Mai: R-Really?
Haruka: Yeah.
Haruka: I think I'm going to become an idol again.
Haruka: I really think that's what I'm meant to be.
Mai: That's great. I'm so glad!
Mai: Does that mean you're going back to the agency? Or have you gotten an offer from somewhere else?
Haruka: I actually haven't thought that far ahead.
Haruka: But I do have an idea...
Mai: Huh?
